title: Moments after Midnights-  A Chaotic Surprise LIVE!
description:
We just did our live listening party, our initial rankings (not yet posted) but this is the chaotic announcement! Live, here's our take on it.. We are heading over to TikTok and Insta live to go discuss! Join us there @the13podcast, and hear our analysis later!
What a chaotic night! And so much fun! Thanks for joining us!
